{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "465bb676-2fbf-41e9-b4e0-023c18cb83f1",
    "name": "Giffgaff-swap-esim_20260409_Fixed",
    "description": "本脚本可以将GiffGaff的实体SIM卡转换为ESIM，无需借助支持ESIM的手机。\n\n---\n\n原脚本由 pwrli大佬制作，由奶昔论坛 [NyaPass7 ](https://forum.naixi.net/space-uid-15488.html) 进行了扩展、修改、适配、更新最新的API与参数等\n\n---\n\n**2026-04-09 更新说明：**\n\n- 修复了CORS错误问题\n    \n- 更新了User-Agent和设备信息到最新版本\n    \n- 添加了手动Token Exchange请求\n    \n- 更新了所有GraphQL请求头\n    \n- 优化了esim相关配置、API接口\n    \n- 更新了最新giffgaff的head头信息\n    \n- 修复了其他版本因各种原因而无法使用的问题",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "53831286",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/53831286-465bb676-2fbf-41e9-b4e0-023c18cb83f1?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "=== OAuth2 认证流程 ===",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "步骤1: 使用pkce-generator.html生成参数",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://id.giffgaff.com/auth/oauth/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=4a05bf219b3985647d9b9a3ba610a9ce&redirect_uri=giffgaff://auth/callback/&scope=read&state={{oauth_state}}&code_challenge={{code_challenge}}&code_challenge_method=S256",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": [
                "id",
                "giffgaff",
                "com"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "oauth",
                "authorize"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "response_type",
                  "value": "code"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "4a05bf219b3985647d9b9a3ba610a9ce"
                },
                {
                  "key": "redirect_uri",
                  "value": "giffgaff://auth/callback/"
                },
                {
                  "key": "scope",
                  "value": "read"
                },
                {
                  "key": "state",
                  "value": "{{oauth_state}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "code_challenge",
                  "value": "{{code_challenge}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "code_challenge_method",
                  "value": "S256"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "【重要】请先使用 pkce-generator.html 生成参数！\n\n使用方法：\n\n1. 在浏览器中打开 pkce-generator.html 文件\n    \n2. 点击 \"生成参数\" 按钮\n    \n3. 将生成的值填入Postman的集合变量中：\n    - code_verifier ← Code Verifier\n        \n    - code_challenge ← Code Challenge\n        \n    - oauth_state ← State\n        \n4. 在HTML工具中点击 \"在新标签页打开授权URL\"\n    \n5. 登录Giffgaff账号，获取回调URL中的code\n    \n6. 将code填入 auth_code 变量\n    \n7. 然后执行步骤2: 交换Token"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "步骤2: 交换Token (使用授权码)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const codeVerifier = pm.collectionVariables.get('code_verifier');",
                  "if (!codeVerifier) {",
                  "    throw new Error('请先执行步骤1获取code_verifier');",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "const code = pm.collectionVariables.get('auth_code');",
                  "if (!code) {",
                  "    throw new Error('请在变量 auth_code 中填入从步骤1获取的授权码');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (response.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', response.access_token);",
                  "    console.log('Access Token 已保存');",
                  "}",
                  "if (response.refresh_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', response.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "User-Agent",
                "value": "giffgaff/1332 CFNetwork/1568.300.101 Darwin/24.2.0",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic NGEwNWJmMjE5YjM5ODU2NDdkOWI5YTNiYTYxMGE5Y2U6T1F2NGNmaXlvbDhUdkNXNHlpTEdqMGMxQWtUUjNOMkpmUnpxN1hHcU14az0=",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "authorization_code",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "code",
                  "value": "{{auth_code}}",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "redirect_uri",
                  "value": "giffgaff://auth/callback/",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "code_verifier",
                  "value": "{{code_verifier}}",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://id.giffgaff.com/auth/oauth/token",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": [
                "id",
                "giffgaff",
                "com"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "oauth",
                "token"
              ]
            },
            "description": "使用从步骤1获取的授权码交换access token\n\n注意：需要先在变量 auth_code 中填入授权码"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "步骤3: 刷新Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (response.access_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', response.access_token);",
                  "}",
                  "if (response.refresh_token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', response.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "User-Agent",
                "value": "giffgaff/1332 CFNetwork/1568.300.101 Darwin/24.2.0",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic NGEwNWJmMjE5YjM5ODU2NDdkOWI5YTNiYTYxMGE5Y2U6T1F2NGNmaXlvbDhUdkNXNHlpTEdqMGMxQWtUUjNOMkpmUnpxN1hHcU14az0=",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "refresh_token",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "key": "refresh_token",
                  "value": "{{refresh_token}}",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "https://id.giffgaff.com/auth/oauth/token",
              "protocol": "https",
              "host": [
                "id",
                "giffgaff",
                "com"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
